{"tid":2489750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警察學院開放日  記者戴黑色口罩遭要求除下 公共關係科:「總之今日黑色就唔得，你一係除，一係遮，唔好同我講咁多。」","createTime":"2021-04-15T06:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T11:17:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":48,"dislike":324,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"3d051d5405caf96a020087225e76eed1e4da1572","tid":2489750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet/12767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet%2F12767&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=e5547cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet/12767</a><br />\n<br />\n#國安教育日 警察學院開放日  記者戴黑色口罩遭要求除下<br />\n<br />\n今日是「全民國家安全教育日」，紀律部隊5間訓練學校配合舉行開放日。傳媒下午到位於黃竹坑的警察學院採訪，警務處處長鄧炳強出席下午的開幕禮，記者在進入學院時，被警員要求除下黑色口罩，至少三名記者需更換口罩。<br />\n<br />\n在場的警察公共關係科表示，在警察學院內不可戴上黑色口罩。有記者一度追問原因，警員表示，「總之今日黑色就唔得，你一係除，一係遮，唔好同我講咁多。」警方更提供其他顏色的口罩予記者更換，「你一係戴我呢個，一係遮咗佢。」"},{"pid":"369940f7257c8431cdfca80339457c620c9e97de","tid":2489750,"uid":246118,"like":350,"dislike":2,"score":348,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:26.000Z","msg":"頭髮黑色，要唔要剪曬去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eae6b114c7b5964effe6cef5aab189f548ab2e2","tid":2489750,"uid":361751,"like":150,"dislike":0,"score":150,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"白色=白票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a993f9ffae45b745e140ef4683a414d123206e94","tid":2489750,"uid":11291,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"戴咩色口罩關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b42af868b0f168fdfd6ffe27d737a849c833ced","tid":2489750,"uid":58630,"like":165,"dislike":1,"score":164,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:56