plyTime":"2021-04-15T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"on9到咁，光字啊乜乜柒柒以後del左佢啊笨"},{"pid":"41b0aeb8910e73b8a9ecb97b12b0f7408fc39259","tid":2489750,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"歧視黑人？"},{"pid":"c14762668cc6b54b0369435bb85b25ae37991fdb","tid":2489750,"uid":324974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">black lives matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7a149e012d40d3fdf1d99b3da8bc93b0b8679232","tid":2489750,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d051d5405caf96a020087225e76eed1e4da1572","tid":2489750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet/12767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet%2F12767&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=e5547cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet/12767</a><br />\n<br />\n#國安教育日 警察學院開放日  記者戴黑色口罩遭要求除下<br />\n<br />\n今日是「全民國家安全教育日」，紀律部隊5間訓練學校配合舉行開放日。傳媒下午到位於黃竹坑的警察學院採訪，警務處處長鄧炳強出席下午的開幕禮，記者在進入學院時，被警員要求除下黑色口罩，至少三名記者需更換口罩。<br />\n<br />\n在場的警察公共關係科表示，在警察學院內不可戴上黑色口罩。有記者一度追問原因，警員表示，「總之今日黑色就唔得，你一係除，一係遮，唔好同我講咁多。」警方更提供其他顏色的口罩予記者更換，「你一係戴我呢個，一係遮咗佢。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"980faca0a499b4cb13e59be46da99cd70d87cb53","tid":2489750,"uid":76471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a993f9ffae45b745e140ef4683a414d123206e94","tid":2489750,"uid":11291,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"戴咩色口罩關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.g